data.text:
Birthday wishes go out to Matt LeBlanc, D.B. Woodside and all the other celebrities with birthdays today. Check out our slideshow below to see photos of famous people turning a year older on July 25th and learn an interesting fact about each of them.

Top celebrity birthdays on July 25, 2024

Model and actress Iman turns 69

Fun fact: Has made guest appearances on TV shows including ‘227′ and ‘Miami Vice’

Actor Matt LeBlanc turns 57

Fun fact: Has a daughter named Marina

Actor D.B. Woodside turns 55

Fun fact: D.B. stands for David Bryan

Actress Meg Donnelly turns 23

Fun fact: Served as the understudy for one of the Von Trapp children in ‘The Sound of Music Live’ TV special
